<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hurt-n">hurt <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /hɜːt/    美 /hɜːrt/  </p>
<p>[U] &amp; [C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[非正式用语]创伤；伤痛：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The hurt in my foot became worse.
我的脚伤更严重了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It was a real hurt to his feelings.
这真的伤害了他的感情。</p></div></div>